                    School Internet Manager Over Networks

                                    SIMON
     __________________________________________________________________

   SIMON is a unique suite of internet tools for K-12 teachers and
       students that facilitates internet searching and the use of
       web-based materials in the school.   SIMON features:

     * Search & Retrieve Functions

     * off-line searching
     * off-line browsing of search results
     * downloading of web sites

     Lesson Building Functions
     * off-line browsing of web sites

     * lesson builder with web page selector
     * lesson editor

     Lesson Library Management
     * off-line lesson library
     * automatic or manual lesson addition
     * lesson sharing utilities
     __________________________________________________________________

